  "topic": "Solubility Equilibrium",
  "question": "For Ag\u2082SO\u2084(s) \u21cc 2Ag\u207a + SO\u2084\u00b2\u207b, what is Ksp?",
  "options": {
    "A": "[Ag\u207a][SO\u2084\u00b2\u207b]",
    "B": "[Ag\u207a]\u00b2[SO\u2084\u00b2\u207b]",
    "C": "[Ag\u207a]\u00b2[SO\u2084\u00b2\u207b]/[Ag\u2082SO\u2084]",
    "D": "[Ag\u2082SO\u2084]/[Ag\u207a][SO\u2084\u00b2\u207b]"
  },
  "answer": "B",
  "explanation": "Ksp = [Ag\u207a]\u00b2[SO\u2084\u00b2\u207b]. Each concentration raised to power of stoichiometric coefficient."
